title: 15 More Books - June 2014 (gnv64)
description:
Another collection of 15 books for this month - 5 PDFs & 10 ePUBs.
Covers are included in a separate folder.

01. Astrophysics Through Computation - With Mathematica Support
02. Bold They Rise - The Space Shuttle Early Years, 1972-1986
03. Buddhist Biology - Ancient Eastern Wisdom Meets Modern Western Science
04. Final Voyage - The World's Worst Maritime Disasters
05. Fortune Tellers - The Story of America's First Economic Forecasters
06. Omics in Soil Science
07. Past, Present, and Future of Statistical Science
08. Saints and Symposiasts - The Literature of Food & the Symposium in Greco-Roman & Early Christian Culture
09. So You Want to Sing Music Theater - A Guide for Professionals
10. The Admiral and the Ambassador - One Man's Obsessive Search for the Body of John Paul Jones
11. The French Intifada - The Long War Between France and Its Arabs
12. To the Edge of the World - The Story of the Trans-Siberian Railway
13. Wonder Woman Unbound - The Curious History of the Worlds Most Famous Heroine
14. Work Smarts - What CEOs Say You Need To Know to Get Ahead
15. Zero - The Biography of a Dangerous Idea
